author: KEXP
description: Swiss sibling duo L'Eclair offer sun-soaked funk on their latest release 'CLOUD DRIFTER'. Their nostalgic yet fresh sound takes to the KEXP Studios with a charged performance of "VERTIGO" and more from across their discography.
title: L'Eclair performs "VERTIGO" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents L'Eclair performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded November 6, 2025.

Songs:  
VERTIGO
Unreleased 1
Unreleased 2
ODESSOS
NOVA UMBRA

Stefan Lilov - Guitar, Synth
Yavor Lilov - Drums, MPC
Charlie Chimi - Percussion, Sampler
Jose Aybar - Bass
Benjamin Hoffman - Keyboards, Synth

Host: Jewel Loree
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Guest Audio Engineer: Steven Mashaka
Audio Mixer: Yavor Lilov 
Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks, Brady Harvey & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht
